snippet.title: Unleashed Trailer: Power Star Game
snippet.description:
Game has been released:  https://www.newgrounds.com/portal/view/912322


Unleash relentless force, wield the might of destruction, obliterate countless Toads, leave Luigi in ruins, and seize control of the Power Stars.

The game will release in beta stage on Newgrounds, on the 31st of December 2023.


Music by @SamuelVirkola 
Newgrounds: https://snvplayer.newgrounds.com/

For more information and updates, visit the Power Star official discord: https://discord.gg/8ktUYRqEmA
